*美国培训与开发协会最优奖<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.astd.org/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-02-06 |archive-date=1996-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/19961029102610/http://www.astd.org/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
